;</foreign> acc. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">υἱέα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:350\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.350</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IGRom.\">IGRom.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.360.29</biblScope> </bibl> (Pergam., hex.)), elsewh. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">υἱόν</foreign> (very freq.): pl., nom. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">υἱέες</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.10</biblScope></bibl></cit>, al., or <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">υἱεῖς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:15:248\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.248</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:24:387\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.387</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:497\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">497</biblScope> </bibl>; gen. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">υἱῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:587\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.587</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:44\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\